# Design System

## Palette CSS
```css
:root {
  --color-nuit:       #1A1612;
  --color-nuit-2:     #231F1A;
  --color-nuit-3:     #2C2620;
  --color-champagne:  #F5E6C8;
  --color-sable:      #F0E0C4;
  --color-or:         #C9A84C;
  --color-or-hover:   #E2C06A;
  --color-or-dim:     rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
  --color-rose-gold:  #B76E79;
  --color-muted:      #7a6e64;
  --color-border:     rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
  --color-border-strong: rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
  --font-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
  --font-body:    'Satoshi', 'Inter', sans-serif;
}
```

## Bouton primaire
```tsx
className="bg-[#C9A84C] text-[#1A1612] font-semibold text-sm px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E2C06A] transition-all duration-200 tracking-wide uppercase"
```

## Input luxe
```tsx
className="w-full bg-[#2C2620] border border-[rgba(201,168,76,0.2)] text-[#F5E6C8] placeholder:text-[#7a6e64] rounded-lg px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#C9A84C] transition-colors"
```
